<TITLE>avicloseall</TITLE>
<TYPE>SIVP Toolbox</TYPE>
<DATE>April, 2006</DATE>
<SHORT_DESCRIPTION name="avicloseall">Close all opened video files/cameras. (experimental)</SHORT_DESCRIPTION>
<CALLING_SEQUENCE>
   <CALLING_SEQUENCE_ITEM>avicloseall()</CALLING_SEQUENCE_ITEM>
</CALLING_SEQUENCE>
<DESCRIPTION>
<P>
   <TT>avicloseall</TT> close all opened video files or cameras.
</P>
<P>
Video support for SIVP is only available when SIVP is compiled with OpenCV which support video I/O.
</P>

</DESCRIPTION>
<EXAMPLE><![CDATA[
	
    n = aviopen(SCI+'/contrib/sivp/images/video.avi');
    im = avireadframe(n); //get a frame
    imshow(im);

    avilistopened()
    aviclose(n);

]]></EXAMPLE>
